                "invention-title": [
                    "Combustion method of ammonia-to-hydrogen internal combustion engine and internal combustion engine",
                    "氨制氢内燃机燃烧方法及内燃机"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the field of internal combustion engines, and provides an ammonia-to-hydrogen internal combustion engine combustion method and an internal combustion engine, the ammonia-to-hydrogen internal combustion engine combustion method comprises the steps that hydrogen is injected into a jet flow chamber, ignition is conducted in the jet flow chamber, liquid ammonia is injected into a combustion chamber for the first time, and the jet flow chamber is communicated with the combustion chamber through a jet flow hole; and liquid ammonia is sprayed into the combustion chamber for the second time. The defect of irregular knocking of hydrogen in a combustion chamber in the prior art is overcome. According to the combustion method of the ammonia-to-hydrogen internal combustion engine, hydrogen is jetted into the jet flow chamber and ignited, high-energy hydrogen flames are formed, the flames are jetted into the combustion chamber through the jet flow holes, liquid ammonia is jetted into the combustion chamber for the first time, under ignition of the flames, the liquid ammonia is subjected to layering, rich combustion and cracking to generate hydrogen, and large-area hydrogen flames are achieved; the liquid ammonia is jetted for the second time to absorb heat and cool the combustion chamber to form an anti-detonation atmosphere, detonation caused by hydrogen spontaneous combustion is inhibited, and the heat efficiency and stability of the internal combustion engine are improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及内燃机领域，提供一种氨制氢内燃机燃烧方法及内燃机，其中，氨制氢内燃机燃烧方法，包括：向射流室内喷射氢气，在所述射流室内点火，向燃烧室内第一次喷射液氨，其中，所述射流室与所述燃烧室通过射流孔连通；向所述燃烧室内第二次喷射液氨。用以解决现有技术中燃烧室内氢的不规则爆震的缺陷。本发明提供的氨制氢内燃机燃烧方法，通过向射流室内喷射氢气，并点火引燃氢气，形成高能氢火焰，并通过射流孔将火焰喷射至燃烧室内，燃烧室内第一次喷射液氨，在火焰的引燃下，液氨分层富燃，裂解产生氢气，实现大面积氢火焰；第二次喷射液氨，对燃烧室内吸热降温，形成抗爆震氛围，抑制氢自燃引发的爆震，提升内燃机的热效率和稳定性。"
                }
